original_title: DJ Ant-Lo & Master P present No Limit Records Video Collection DVD
overview: Master P performs in the music video "Make 'Em Say Uhh!" from the album "Ghetto D" recorded for No Limit Records and Priority Records. Master P raps as he sits atop a golden tank in the middle of a basketball court. He is joined in his performance by Fiend, Silkk the Shocker, Mia X and Mystikal.
title: DJ Ant-Lo & Master P present No Limit Records Video Collection DVD
